com.samskivert.depot

Class Key<T extends PersistentRecord>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samskivert.depot.clause.WhereClause
      • com.samskivert.depot.Key<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CacheInvalidator, QueryClause, SQLFragment, ValidatingCacheInvalidator

    public class Key<T extends PersistentRecord>
extends WhereClause
implements ValidatingCacheInvalidator
    A special form of WhereClause that uniquely specifies a single database row and thus also a single persistent object. It knows how to invalidate itself upon modification. This class is created by many DepotMarshaller methods as a convenience, and may also be instantiated explicitly.
